<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Duplicate on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/duplicate/</link><description>Recent content in Duplicate on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/duplicate/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] Linux ENOTUNIQ (errno 55) — Name Not Unique on Network Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/os/linux/errno-55/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/os/linux/errno-55/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="linux-enotuniq-errno-55--name-not-unique-on-network"&gt;Linux ENOTUNIQ (errno 55) — Name Not Unique on Network&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ENOTUNIQ (errno 55) means the name is not unique on the network. This error occurs when a program tries to register a network name (such as a hostname or service name) that is already in use by another machine on the network. It is distinct from EADDRINUSE (errno 98) because ENOTUNIQ specifically refers to name uniqueness, not address port binding.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] SQLite UNIQUE Constraint Failed</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/sqlite/constraint-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/sqlite/constraint-error/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="sqlite-unique-constraint-failed"&gt;SQLite UNIQUE Constraint Failed&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A UNIQUE constraint failure occurs when an INSERT or UPDATE attempts to add a value that already exists in a column with a UNIQUE constraint or PRIMARY KEY.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Attempting to insert a duplicate primary key value&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A column with a UNIQUE constraint already contains the value&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Race condition in concurrent inserts without proper locking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The application logic does not check for existing records&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="use-insert-or-replace"&gt;Use INSERT OR REPLACE&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INSERT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;OR&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;REPLACE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INTO&lt;/span&gt; users (id, name, email)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;VALUES&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;Alice&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;alice@example.com&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="use-insert-or-ignore-to-skip-duplicates"&gt;Use INSERT OR IGNORE to Skip Duplicates&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INSERT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;OR&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;IGNORE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INTO&lt;/span&gt; users (id, name, email)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;VALUES&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;Alice&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;alice@example.com&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="use-upsert-insert-on-conflict"&gt;Use UPSERT (INSERT ON CONFLICT)&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INSERT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INTO&lt;/span&gt; users (id, name, email)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;VALUES&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;Alice&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;alice@example.com&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;ON&lt;/span&gt; CONFLICT(id) &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;DO&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;UPDATE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SET&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; name &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; excluded.name,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; email &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; excluded.email;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="check-existing-values-before-insert"&gt;Check Existing Values Before Insert&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Check if the value already exists
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SELECT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;COUNT&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt; users &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;WHERE&lt;/span&gt; id &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- If count &amp;gt; 0, use UPDATE instead of INSERT
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="add-auto-increment-for-primary-keys"&gt;Add Auto-Increment for Primary Keys&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;CREATE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;TABLE&lt;/span&gt; users (
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; id INTEGER &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;PRIMARY&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;KEY&lt;/span&gt; AUTOINCREMENT,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; name TEXT &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;NOT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;NULL&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; email TEXT &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;UNIQUE&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Duplicate primary key
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INSERT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INTO&lt;/span&gt; users (id, name) &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;VALUES&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;Alice&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INSERT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INTO&lt;/span&gt; users (id, name) &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;VALUES&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;Bob&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Error: UNIQUE constraint failed: users.id
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Duplicate unique email
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INSERT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;INTO&lt;/span&gt; users (id, name, email) &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;VALUES&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;Bob&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;alice@example.com&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Error: UNIQUE constraint failed: users.email
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/sqlite/constraint-error/"&gt;Constraint Error&lt;/a&gt; — other constraint violations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/sqlite/database-locked/"&gt;Database Locked&lt;/a&gt; — write lock contention&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] Systemd Unit is Already Active</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/systemd/already-active/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/systemd/already-active/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="systemd-unit-is-already-active"&gt;Systemd Unit is Already Active&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This error occurs when you try to start a systemd unit that is already in an active state. Systemd prevents duplicate activation unless the unit is configured for it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The service is already running and start was called again&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A timer or socket triggered the service while it was active&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The unit file lacks &lt;code&gt;RemainAfterExit=yes&lt;/code&gt; for services that exit cleanly&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Multiple automation scripts are trying to start the same service&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="check-current-unit-status"&gt;Check Current Unit Status&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;systemctl status &amp;lt;service-name&amp;gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="use-restart-instead-of-start"&gt;Use Restart Instead of Start&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo systemctl restart &amp;lt;service-name&amp;gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="check-for-duplicate-triggers"&gt;Check for Duplicate Triggers&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;systemctl list-timers --all
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;systemctl list-sockets --all
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="allow-repeated-activation-with-remainafterexit"&gt;Allow Repeated Activation with RemainAfterExit&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-ini" data-lang="ini"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;[Service]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Type&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;oneshot&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;RemainAfterExit&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;yes&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;ExecStart&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;/usr/bin/my-setup-script&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="mask-the-service-if-it-should-not-run"&gt;Mask the Service If It Should Not Run&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo systemctl mask &amp;lt;service-name&amp;gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Attempting to start an already running service&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo systemctl start nginx
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Failed to start nginx: Unit nginx.service is already active.&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Fix: use systemctl restart nginx&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Timer triggered while service was active&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Fix: check timers with systemctl list-timers&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/systemd/not-found8/"&gt;Not Found&lt;/a&gt; — unit does not exist&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/systemd/reload-error/"&gt;Reload Error&lt;/a&gt; — service failed to reload configuration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>E11000 duplicate key error collection</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/mongodb/duplicate-key/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/mongodb/duplicate-key/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;This error occurs when you try to insert or update a document with a value that already exists in a unique index field. MongoDB enforces uniqueness constraints and rejects the operation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Inserting a document with a &lt;code&gt;_id&lt;/code&gt; or unique field that already exists&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Missing application-level checks for duplicates&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Race condition where two processes insert the same key simultaneously&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Unintended unique index on a field that should allow duplicates&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use upsert to insert-or-update:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;db&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;users&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;updateOne&lt;/span&gt;(
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; { &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;email&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;user@example.com&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; },
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; { &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;$setOnInsert&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; { &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Alice&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; } },
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; { &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;upsert&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;true&lt;/span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="2"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Check existing unique indexes:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;db&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;collection&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;getIndexes&lt;/span&gt;()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="3"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Remove an unintended unique index if needed:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;db&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;collection&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;dropIndex&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;fieldname_1&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="4"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Wrap inserts in a try-catch and handle duplicates gracefully:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;try&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;await&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;db&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;users&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;insertOne&lt;/span&gt;({ &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;_id&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;user123&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Alice&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; });
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;} &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;catch&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;e&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;e&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;code&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;===&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;11000&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;console&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;log&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Duplicate key, skipping insert&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; } &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;else&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;throw&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;e&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// First insert succeeds
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;db&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;users&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;insertOne&lt;/span&gt;({ &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;_id&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;user1&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Alice&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; });
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Second insert fails with E11000
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;db&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;users&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;insertOne&lt;/span&gt;({ &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;_id&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;user1&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;name&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Bob&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; });
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// E11000 duplicate key error collection: mydb.users dup key: { _id: &amp;#34;user1&amp;#34; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/mongodb/connection-refused"&gt;Connection Refused&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>ERROR 1050 (42S01): Table 'X' already exists</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/mysql/table-exists/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/mysql/table-exists/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;This error occurs when you try to create a table with a name that already exists in the database.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Running CREATE TABLE twice with the same name&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Script executed multiple times without idempotency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Migration rerun without DROP TABLE&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Schema drift between environments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use &lt;code&gt;IF NOT EXISTS&lt;/code&gt; to avoid the error:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;CREATE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;TABLE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;IF&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;NOT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;EXISTS&lt;/span&gt; mytable (
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; id INT &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;PRIMARY&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;KEY&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; name VARCHAR(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;255&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="2"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Check if the table exists:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SHOW&lt;/span&gt; TABLES &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;LIKE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;mytable&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="3"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drop the existing table if needed:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;DROP&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;TABLE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;IF&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;EXISTS&lt;/span&gt; mytable;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- This will fail if mytable already exists
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;CREATE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;TABLE&lt;/span&gt; mytable (id INT &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;PRIMARY&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;KEY&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Error output:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- ERROR 1050 (42S01): Table &amp;#39;mytable&amp;#39; already exists
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Safe approach:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;CREATE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;TABLE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;IF&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;NOT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;EXISTS&lt;/span&gt; mytable (id INT &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;PRIMARY&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;KEY&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Check if table exists via command line&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;mysql -e &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;SHOW TABLES LIKE &amp;#39;mytable&amp;#39;;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; mydb
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Create only if not exists&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;mysql -e &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS mytable (id INT);&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; mydb
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/mysql/access-denied"&gt;Access Denied&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/postgresql/database-exists"&gt;Database Already Exists&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>ERROR: database "X" already exists</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/postgresql/database-exists/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/postgresql/database-exists/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;This error occurs when you try to create a database with a name that is already taken in the PostgreSQL cluster.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Running CREATE DATABASE twice with the same name&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Script executed multiple times without idempotency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Typo in database name (e.g., trying to create &amp;ldquo;mydb&amp;rdquo; when &amp;ldquo;mydb&amp;rdquo; exists)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Schema migration rerun without drop&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use &lt;code&gt;IF NOT EXISTS&lt;/code&gt; to avoid the error:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;CREATE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;DATABASE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;IF&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;NOT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;EXISTS&lt;/span&gt; mydb;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="2"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;List existing databases to verify the name:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;SELECT&lt;/span&gt; datname &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt; pg_database &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;WHERE&lt;/span&gt; datname &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;mydb&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="3"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drop the existing database if needed:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;dropdb mydb
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sql" data-lang="sql"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- This will fail if mydb already exists
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;CREATE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;DATABASE&lt;/span&gt; mydb;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Error output:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- ERROR: database &amp;#34;mydb&amp;#34; already exists
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;-- Safe approach:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;CREATE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;DATABASE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;IF&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;NOT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;EXISTS&lt;/span&gt; mydb;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Check if database exists&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;psql -l | grep mydb
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Create only if not exists&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;createdb mydb &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;||&lt;/span&gt; echo &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Database already exists&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/postgresql/connection-refused"&gt;Connection Refused&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/mysql/table-exists"&gt;Table Already Exists&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>